    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《</strong>造物主 2<strong>》</strong>中，再次成为神灵，指挥控制强大的巨人，他们操控元素的力量能让你塑造世界，创造资源生态系统，并让人类文明蓬勃发展。你的选择将决定这些脆弱人类的命运，给他们自主权的话，人类文明可能可以因此达到巅峰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>派出巨人塑造世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/d360ba0fccc49abe1fc90b3c7aa4937e.poster.avif?t=1769093803\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/d360ba0fccc49abe1fc90b3c7aa4937e.webm?t=1769093803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/d360ba0fccc49abe1fc90b3c7aa4937e.mp4?t=1769093803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用6名强大的巨人，每个巨人都具备有关植物、动物和矿物的独特能力，让你能够为人类营造新的生态环境。随着你累积游戏进度，可获得灵感解锁更多巨人技能，为你提供多样化的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关系与灾难</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着 !<strong>新大灾变更新</strong>!，你可以选择接受更多可选挑战。领袖现在可以根据其个性与巨人和其他领袖建立关系，通过贸易结成同盟或发动战争。人类也可能反抗你的巨人，派出巨人猎手来摧毁他们！使用全新的灾难之力惩罚他们，利用元素之力让他们学会尊重神灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造繁荣的生态系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/b80df40a6fb03b9aa2775d1e99258a7e.poster.avif?t=1769093803\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/b80df40a6fb03b9aa2775d1e99258a7e.webm?t=1769093803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/b80df40a6fb03b9aa2775d1e99258a7e.mp4?t=1769093803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对各种生态环境进行改造，策略性地打造不同组合且与环境息息相关的植物、动物和材料。通过实验，看看哪些组合最能够满足居民的需求和目标，引领他们迈向辉煌新时代。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>引领人类走向未来</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/869923f8739ece294c071cfd9f7187b1.poster.avif?t=1769093803\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/869923f8739ece294c071cfd9f7187b1.webm?t=1769093803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/869923f8739ece294c071cfd9f7187b1.mp4?t=1769093803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过你的选择塑造人类文明的发展，从原始部落进化为先进文明。无论是作为太空探索者穿越星际，创建邪教，还是培育自然，他们都有自己的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论结果如何，请记住，你总是可以重新开始新的人类文明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让星系充满生命</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/49490aac2e962c74a9b94f940b7c5a00.poster.avif?t=1769093803\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/49490aac2e962c74a9b94f940b7c5a00.webm?t=1769093803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875060/extras/49490aac2e962c74a9b94f940b7c5a00.mp4?t=1769093803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每场游戏过程中，你都会在繁星之间创造一颗新的星球进行实验并留下自己的足迹，让星系中充满各种生命，从中获得灵感，在下次创世的时候来点不一样的发展道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这款游戏得到了荷兰创意产业基金的支持。</strong></p>",
